LGTM - thanks for this great new builtin @OsChri. I just slightly changed the test to use fixed seeds and replaced the for loops for joint sorting of two matrices with vectorized permutation matrix multiplications:
```
reorder = order(target=scoreboard, index.return=TRUE);
P = table(seq(1,n_i), reorder); # permutation matrix
scoreboard = P %*% scoreboard;
candidateWeights = P %*% candidateWeights;
```

@sebwrede 
Now it should work all the time with any tolerance. If you want to try again!

Otherwise if it LGT(you) then i will merge.
